sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as Coordinator
    participant PR as Paper Reader
    participant RE as Research Explainer
    participant FC as Fact Checker
    participant RW as Related Work
    participant RG as Research Gap
    participant QT as Quiz/Teaching
    participant PA as Presentation
    participant M as Memory

    U->>C: Upload PDF / request analysis
    C->>C: PLAN execution across agents
    C->>PR: DELEGATE: extract & segment paper
    PR->>PR: EXECUTE -> VERIFY -> REFLECT
    PR->>C: Structured paper

    C->>RE: DELEGATE: generate summaries
    RE->>C: Executive / Technical / Beginner / ELI5

    C->>FC: DELEGATE: verify claims
    FC->>C: Verified / Questionable / Needs Review + confidence

    FC->>RW: HANDOFF: discover related work
    RW->>RG: HANDOFF: identify gaps from related context
    RG->>QT: (parallel) Coordinator dispatches study materials
    RG->>PA: HANDOFF: build presentation from gap analysis

    PA->>C: Final presentation pack
    C->>M: STORE: paper summary + insights
    C->>U: RESPOND: aggregated final report + human-review notice
